{"word":"G3684 - ὀνικός - onikós - on-ik-os' - Millstone","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὀνικός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">onikós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">on-ik-os'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Millstone</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சிறியரான, சிறுவரான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"of or for an ass"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3688 - ὄνος - ónos - on'-os/3688\">G3688</a>; <i>belonging to</i> an <i>ass</i>, that is, <i>large</i> (so as to be turned by an ass): - millstone.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}